name: User Login Details
query:
SELECT 
`tabUser`.name as "ID:Link/User:150",
`tabUser`.first_name as "Name:Data:120",
`tabUser`.login_after as "Login After:Data:80",
`tabUser`.login_before as "Login Before:Data:80",
`tabUser`.restrict_ip as "Login IP:Data:110",
`tabUser`.last_ip as "Last IP:Data:110",
`tabUser`.last_login as "Last Login:Data:180",
`tabUser`.last_active as "Last Active:Data:180"

FROM
`tabUser`

WHERE
`tabUser`.enabled=%(status)s
